    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Choose a creature that you can see within range. A surge of positive energy washes through the creature, causing it to regain 70 hit points. This spell also ends &amp;Reference[condition=blinded]{blindness}, &amp;Reference[condition=deafened]{deafness}, and any diseases affecting the target. This spell has no effect on constructs or undead.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p></p><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"At Higher Levels\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">At Higher Levels.</span></span> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the amount of healing increases by 10 for each slot level above 6th.</p></div></div>",
